cloud_oauth_code.description:
Open the authorization link, complete authorization, and enter the code from the callback URL. This step exchanges it for an Access Token and continues to house selection.

Authorization link: {authorization_url}

Domain: {domain}

cloud_scan_login.description:
Open Yeelight APP 1.5.0 or later, go to the scan page, and scan the QR code below to authorize Home Assistant. If scanning fails, enter this content manually: {qrcode}

Status: {status}
Remaining seconds: {remaining_seconds}
Poll count: {poll_count}

After you submit, Home Assistant will continuously poll the scan authorization status. Select refresh after the QR code expires.

